2VvKPMrXHDKwxT05faz4PeRCheqfwQ8mOGZrarXekaUlgw1t4BcozaD1lOCWXyTMZf_u3lkP5eEJs5hovd2VwWx\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering OAuth2WebClient testing**\\n\\nI’m thinking about testing the OAuth2WebClient class. It seems like it might require adding an optional dependency to cover its usage properly. I'm not sure if this is absolutely necessary, but it’s something I should investigate further. I want to ensure that I’m considering all options for compiling the tests effectively. It’s essential to get this right to make the testing process smooth and comprehensive!\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Vert.x Web Client 5.0.1 can be covered with the normal in-process client/server scaffold and no extra dependency or Docker image, but its Netty 4.2.x runtime still needs the Java 25 native-run system properties already used for 5.0.0.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For native-image runtime on JDK 25, ensure the generated test/build setup passes `-Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` and `-Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true` for `io.vertx:vertx-web-client:5.0.1` as well as 5.0.0, preferably by keying the condition to Vert.x/Netty 4.2.x rather than only the exact library version. Use an in-process Vert.x `HttpServer` for request/response, JSON, form, multipart, redirect, cookie/session, and streaming coverage; no external service is required.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The artifact declares `vertx-auth-oauth2` as optional; avoid OAuth2-specific `OAuth2WebClient` tests unless the workflow intentionally adds that dependency.\",\n    \"Local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative for whether the Java 25 Netty system properties fully address the run failure.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01201a4b4e8f97c5016a3ef0c5e570819482365d9e4ec46693\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1747, "output": 1285, "cacheRead": 27136, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30168, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782509751032, "responseId": "resp_01201a4b4e8f97c5016a3ef0b78d308194b76ba6e5becaa2c5"}, "toolResults": []}
